S.description: base load demand not counting child objects, including weather sensitivities, copied to Pd,Qd by default (MVA)

type.description: bus type (1 = PQ, 2 = PV, 3 = ref, 4 = isolated)

Gs.description: shunt conductance (MW at V = 1.0 per unit)

Bs.description: shunt susceptance (MVAr at V = 1.0 per unit)

lam_P.description: Lagrange multiplier on real power mismatch (u/MW)

lam_Q.description: Lagrange multiplier on reactive power mismatch (u/MVAr)

mu_Vmax.description: Kuhn-Tucker multiplier on upper voltage limit (u/per unit)

mu_Vmin.description: Kuhn-Tucker multiplier on lower voltage limit (u/per unit)

status.description: initial branch status, IN=1 - in service, OUT=0 - out of service
initial branch status, IN=1 - in service, OUT=0 - out of service

Pmin.description: lower limit on PF (MW flow at 'from' end)

Pmax.description: upper limit on PF (MW flow at 'from' end)

Qminf.description: lower limit on MVAr injection at 'from' bus

Qmaxf.description: upper limit on MVAr injection at 'from' bus

Qmint.description: lower limit on MVAr injection at  'to'  bus

Qmaxt.description: upper limit on MVAr injection at  'to'  bus

loss0.description: constant term of linear loss function (MW) on Sfrom

loss1.description: linear term of linear loss function (MW/MW) w.r.t Sfrom

mu_Pmin.description: Kuhn-Tucker multiplier on lower flow limit at 'from' bus

mu_Pmax.description: Kuhn-Tucker multiplier on upper flow limit at 'from' bus

mu_Qminf.description: Kuhn-Tucker multiplier on lower VAr limit at 'from' bus

mu_Qmaxf.description: Kuhn-Tucker multiplier on upper VAr limit at 'from' bus

mu_Qmint.description: Kuhn-Tucker multiplier on lower VAr limit at 'to' bus

mu_Qmaxt.description: Kuhn-Tucker multiplier on upper VAr limit at 'to' bus

control.description: Control point at which power flow is regulated

mBase.description: total MVA base of machine, defaults to baseMVA

Pc1.description: lower real power output of PQ capability curve (MW)

Pc2.description: upper real power output of PQ capability curve (MW)

Qc1min.description: minimum reactive power output at Pc1 (MVAr)

Qc1max.description: maximum reactive power output at Pc1 (MVAr)

Qc2min.description: minimum reactive power output at Pc2 (MVAr)

Qc2max.description: maximum reactive power output at Pc2 (MVAr)

ramp_q.description: ramp rate for reactive power (2 sec timescale) (MVAr/min)

mu_Pmax.description: Kuhn-Tucker multiplier on upper Pg limit (per unit/MW)

mu_Pmin.description: Kuhn-Tucker multiplier on lower Pg limit (per unit/MW)

mu_Qmax.description: Kuhn-Tucker multiplier on upper Qg limit (per unit/MVAr)

mu_Qmin.description: Kuhn-Tucker multiplier on lower Qg limit (per unit/MVAr)

target.description: geodata target class and property, e.g., CLASS::PROPERTY or OBJECT.PROPERTY

scale.description: scale to apply to geodata values in file before writing to target

response.description: curtailment response as fractional load reduction

city.description: City in which powerplant is located

state.description: State in which powerplant is located

zipcode.description: Zipcode in which powerplant is located

country.description: Country in which powerplant is located

point.description: Enable access to point specified as object <name>:<property>

record.description: Enable recording of point to historian

steps_1.description: numbers of steps in control block 1

admittance_1.description: control block 1 shunt admittance step at unity voltage

steps_2.description: number of steps in control block 2

admittance_2.description: control block 2 shunt admittance step at unity voltage

steps_3.description: number of steps in control block 3

admittance_3.description: control block 3 shunt admittance step at unity voltage

steps_4.description: number of steps in control block 4

admittance_4.description: control block 4 shunt admittance step at unity voltage

steps_5.description: number of steps in control block 5

admittance_5.description: control block 5 shunt admittance step at unity voltage

steps_6.description: number of steps in control block 6

admittance_6.description: control block 6 shunt admittance step at unity voltage

steps_7.description: number of steps in control block 7

admittance_7.description: control block 7 shunt admittance step at unity voltage

steps_8.description: number of steps in control block 8

admittance_8.description: control block 8 shunt admittance step at unity voltage

phase_shift.description: transformer phase shift (deg) - use 30 for DY or YD transformers
